\id JUD - Asang Khongca Bible (2019) 
\h Juda 
\toc1 Juda 
\toc2 Juda 
\toc3 Jud 
\mt1 JUDA  
\ipq Hae cabu tarikkung Juda loe Jesu ih amnawk kalang mue, tiah poekhaih tawnh o (Mat. 13.55). Juda loe Gnostic angsahcop long palunghahaih bangah amtuk kasang kaminawk mah patuk ih amro kaminawk kawng to thuih. To patukhaih loe saning cumvaito boeng khoek to poek hankoi kaom thacak patukhaih maeto ah oh. Juda capat thung ih lok loe Piter capat hnetto thung ih loknawk hoiah anghmong. Juda capat thungah loe Baibul na ai ah kalah cabunawk kawng thuihhaih vai hnetto amtueng (kathoeng 9-14). Paroeai kaciim tanghaih to a qoeng o sak thai hanah, ca kroek kaminawk thapaekhaih lok to a hnuk o. Hae capat loe A.D 65-67 ai naah tarik kalang boeh mue, tiah poekhaih tawnh o.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Mathai 13.55; Mark 6.3.\x*Ampa Sithaw mah ciimcaisak ih, Jesu Kri mah pakuem moe, kawk ih kaminawk khaeah, Jesu Kri tamna ah kaom, Jakob ih amnawk, Juda mah tarik:  
\v 2 palungnathaih, monghaih hoi amlunghaih nangcae khaeah pung nasoe.  
\v 3 Palung ih kaminawk, kami boih han kaom pahlonghaih kawng nangcae khaeah tarik moe, paek hanah tha ka pathok, toe kaciim kaminawk khaeah vaito kakhawt ah paek ih tanghaih to na pakaa o hanah ca tarik han angaih, tiah ka poek.  
\v 4 Lokcaek hanah canghni hoi pahoe coek ih Sithaw panoek ai thoemto kaminawk loe, tamquta hoi akun o moe, aicae Sithaw tahmenhaih to nongpata nongpa zaehaih bangah paqoi o ving, maeto khue kaom Angraeng Sithaw hoi aicae Angraeng Jesu Kri to tapom han koeh o ai.   
\s1 Kamro patukkungnawk  
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt EXO 12.51; \xt NAM 14.29,30.\x*Angraeng mah angmah ih kaminawk to Izip prae thung hoiah pahlong, toe anih mah hnukkhuem ah tang ai kaminawk to hum, tiah kaom hmuen kawng hae na panoek o boih boeh e, panoeksak let han ka koeh.  
\v 6 Hmaloe koekah angmacae angdoethaih ahmuen ah kaom poe ai, angmacae ohhaih ahmuen caehtaak vankaminawk to, kalen parai niah lokcaek hanah Anih mah sumqui hoi dungzan ah pathlet moe, khoving thungah suek boeh.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Genesis 19.1-24.\x*To baktih toengah, Sodom hoi Gomorrah taeng ih vangpuinawk doeh, nongpa nongpata zae sakhaih bangah ang paek o moe, angmacae zu sava na ai kalah kaminawk hoiah zaehaih a sak o pongah, khet koi kaom ah dungzan hmai hoiah lokcaekhaih to a tongh o.  
\v 8 To baktih toengah hae tiah amaang sah kaminawk mah doeh angmacae ih takpum to panuet kaom ah a sak o, ukhaih to pahnawt o ai, ukhaih kaa tawn kaminawk to kasae a thuih o.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Dan 10.13,21; 12.1; Lph 12.7; \xt Deu 34.6; \xt Zek 3.2.\x*Toe kalen koek van kami Mikal mah mataeng doeh, Setan hoiah Mosi ih takpum anglomh hoi naah, anih to kasae thuih han zit pongah, Angraeng mah na thuitaek nasoe, tiah a naa.  
\v 10 Toe hae kaminawk mah loe nihcae mah panoek ai ih hmuennawk to kasae thuih o: moi kasan baktiah angmacae mah panoek o ih hmuennawk hoiah angmacae to amrosak.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Genesis 4.3-8; \xt NAM 22.1-35; \xt NAM 16.1-35.\x*Khosak na bing o! Nihcae loe Kain ih loklam ni pazui o boeh, amekhaih hnuk han koeh o pongah Balaam sakpazaehaih thungah akun o moe, Kore lokaekhaih thungah amro o boih boeh.  
\v 12 To kaminawk loe na koeh o ih poihkung ah, nangcae hoi nawnto buhcaak naah, azathaih tawn ai ah angmacae koeh karoek to buh to a caak o: nihcae loe takhi mah koeh baktiah hmuh ih, khotui kaom ai tamainawk baktiah ni oh o; athaih athai ai, akung kazaem, vai hnetto kadueh, tangzun hoi aphong ih thingkung baktih;  
\v 13 kangphui tuipui tuiphunawk baktiah angmacae azathaih to amtueng o sak, dungzan ah khoving tahmuep loe kazawk cakaeh ah kaom nihcae hanah pahoe pae boeh.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Genesis 5.18,21-24.\x*Adam hoi sarihto haih ah kaom Enok mah, Khenah, Angraeng loe angmah ih kaciim kami sang hato hoi nawnto angzo ueloe,  
\v 15 kaminawk boih lokcaek tih, Sithaw panoek ai kaminawk boih mah a sak o ih zaehaih baktih, sethaih kawng kathui kazae kaminawk mah Anih kasae thuih o ih zaehaih baktih toengah lokcaek boih tih.  
\v 16 To kaminawk loe laisaep thaih kami, kasae thui thaih kami, angmacae taksa koehhaih baktiah caeh kami ah oh o; nihcae loe amoekhaih lokthui kami, angmacae amekhaih hnuk hanah minawk pahlaw thaih kami ah oh o.   
\s1 Loktang tanghaih to patawn oh  
\p
\v 17 Toe palung ih kaminawk, Aicae Angraeng Jesu Kri mah patoeh ih kami ah kaom kaminawk mah ang thuih o ih lok to panoek oh;  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt 2 Pt 3.3.\x*nihcae mah nangcae khaeah, Hnukkhuem niah loe, Sithaw koehhaih na ai ah, angmacae taksa koehhaih bangah caeh kaminawk hoi minawk kasae thuih koeh kaminawk to angzo o tih, tiah ang thuih o boeh.  
\v 19 Nihcae loe nangcae tapraek kami, long taksa koehhaih patom kami, Muithla tawn ai kami ah oh o.  
\v 20 Toe palung ih kaminawk, Nangcae loe paroeai ciimcai tanghaih ah qoeng o tahang ah loe, Ciimcai Muithla ah lawkthui oh.  
\v 21 Nangcae loe Sithaw amlunghaih ah om oh loe, dungzan hing hanah aicae Angraeng Jesu Kri palungnathaih to khen oh.  
\v 22 Pathlaeng thaihaih tawn oh loe, thoemto kaminawk tahmenhaih palungthin to tawn oh:  
\v 23 taksa zaehaih kakap khukbuen to hnuma oh, zithaih palungthin hoiah thoemto kaminawk to hmai thung hoiah pahlong oh.   
\s1 Tahamhoih paekhaih  
\p
\v 24 Nangcae amthaek naah pathawkkung, lensawk angmah hmaa ah thuilaek ai anghoehaih hoiah zaehoikung,  
\v 25 lensawkhaih hoi saiqathaih, ukhaih hoi thacakhaih loe palungha aicae pahlongkung Sithaw khae khue ah, vaihi hoi dungzan khoek to om poe nasoe. Amen.   